# Client-side
<client>
<features>
NTLM
</features>
<server>
http
</server>
 <name>
HTTP with NTLM/Negotiate/Basic, anyauth and user with domain, with size 0
 </name>
 <command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/91 --anyauth -u mydomain\\myself:secret
</command>
</client>

